<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hans Halbwachs, Krämer zu Gera</head><p>Der Rat dankt für die Auskunft zu Personen, die bei Angriffen auf Nürnberger beteiligt gewesen sind, und kündigt seine Mitteilung an, wenn er Näheres erfährt.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_493" id="245v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_493_r2l16">Dem <expan>beſchaıd<ex>en</ex></expan> . <expan>Hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> Halpwachſen eınem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_493_r2l17"><expan>Crom<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>geſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>man<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu Gera </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><note place="marginleft"><ab facs="#facs_493_r1l1">Jn bapıro </ab></note>
<ab facs="#facs_493_r2l18"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> hanns als du vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> haſt wıe ein man vıl mıt dır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_493_r2l19">geredt hab von <expan>etlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe bey <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſcheden <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſeyn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_493_r2l20">Darinn du dıch wıllıg erpeẅtſt ʒu beweıſen etc / des <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_493_r2l21">wır dır freẅntlıch / Nu ıſt vns auf dıſʒ ʒeıt nıht wol wıſſend </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_493_r2l22">dauon . doch ſo wellen wır darauf bedacht ſeyn . vnd <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_493_r2l23"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ıcht ʒu rate . das ſol dır wol ʒu wıſſend <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_493_r2l24"><expan>ſ<ex>ubſi</ex></expan> gıllo Erhardȷ ſchurſtab <expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>iſt</ex>rıcıuıu<ex>m</ex></expan> . ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_493" id="245v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem <expan>beschaid<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Halpwachsen, einem
                            <expan>crom<ex>er</ex></expan> und <expan>gesess<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>man<ex>n</ex></expan> zu Gera</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><app>
<note place="marginleft">In bapiro </note>
</app>
<expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Hanns, als du uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hast, wie ein man vil mit dir geredt
                        hab von <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        scheden <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> seyn, darinn du dich willig erpewtst
                        zu beweisen etc., des <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> wir dir frewntlich. Nu
                        ist uns auf disz zeit niht wol wissend davon, doch so wellen wir darauf
                        bedacht seyn und <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> wir
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> icht zu rate, das sol dir wol zu wissend
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>ub si</ex></expan>gillo Erhardi Schurstab
                                <expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>ist</ex>ri</expan>
<expan>civiu<ex>m</ex></expan> ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab></div>
</div></body>
